Description
-=-=-=-=-=-=

Hornby's virtual model railway CD-ROM has been developed in close collaboration with Hornby's model railway experts. The secret of a successful design program is to combine ease of use with high-quality interactive output. Hornby Virtual Railway achieves this and much more.

Additional Details
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

Features:

* Simple and easy to use
* Design in 2D and 3D
* Offers a database full of realistic trains, tracks and scenic models straight from the Hornby Catalogue

System Requirements:

OS: Windows 95/98/2000
Processor: Pentium 2000 MHz
Memory: 32 MB RAM
Video Card: 16 Bit colour 800x600
Sound Card: Windows compatible
DirectX: #
Disk Drive: CD-ROM
Hard Drive: #

Version:

1.0

Website:

www.hornby.com

Price:

#

Installation Details
-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

To install, mount Hornby Virtual Railway.mds and install. To install addons, mount Hornby Virtual Railway Addons.mds and install all three addon packs.
